# NOTE: src/data/recipes.json and public/recipe-images/ are GENERATED by
# scripts/build-data.mjs from the read-only recipe-repo, but they are committed
# on purpose: recipe-repo is not published to GitHub, so the committed bundle is
# what lets a fresh clone / CI build & test without the source. Regenerate and
# re-commit them (`npm run build:data`) whenever recipe-repo changes.
